Class FacebookSnooper

  • java.lang.Object
    • apis.FacebookSnooper

  • public class FacebookSnooper
extends java.lang.Object
    The facebookProfile class is designed to pull data from a user's Facebook profile, including the user's name, profile picture, profile URL, and the posts from that user.

    Author:
